This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. Implements RFC 1952 (GZIP file format specification version
4.3) directly, wrapping swift-deflate for the inner DEFLATE body and
swift-crc for the CRC-32/ISO-HDLC trailer check.

RFC 1952: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc1952.html
